channel.title: Just bought a new computer to host my server and need help -_-
channel.description: Hello, I hosted my server on my other computer but noticed the computer was getting way to slow for me to continue, so I went out and bought an ultra expensive gaming pc, I got back, hooked everything up, took the files and transfered them "via" a brand new flash drive I bought whilst at the store, then I converted the files from the drive to my new computer, I downloaded Java 6 u 21 and set my path and CLASSPATH 6 u 21, I downloaded the No-ip DUC and cranked er on, runs fine, I went to light my server up and it says: 'Java' is not recognised as an internal or external command or operable batch file. The new system is 64.bit, running windows 7. Please help me, I need help fast. Thank you!
